 Ioctl for setting IPIPE parameters.
 
#define VPS_ISS_IPIPE_IOCTL_SET_CONFIG   (VPS_ISS_IPIPE_IOCTL_GET_CONFIG + 1U)
 Ioctl for getting IPIPE parameters.
 
#define VPS_ISS_IPIPE_IOCTL_UPDATE_LUT_FMT   (VPS_ISS_IPIPE_IOCTL_GET_CONFIG + 2U)
 For 3D Lut, the ip LUT format is different. It does not use Red, Green and Blue directly. Instead, ip requires them to be merged in different way and then they can be used. This ioctl is used for converting LUT format.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum vpsissIpipeCfaMode

Valid CFA Modes. Used for selecting algorithm for CFA and to select Digital anti-aliasing filter.

enum vpsissIpipeCfaMode

Enumerator
VPS_ISS_IPIPE_CFA_MODE_2DIRAC 

CFA Mode is 2DirAC

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_CFA_MODE_2DIRAC_DAA 

CFA Mode is 2DirAC plus Digital Antialiasing

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_CFA_MODE_DAA 

CFA Mode is Digital Antialiasing

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_CFA_MODE_COSITED 

CFA Mode is Co-Sited bayer format, the sampling points of R/Gr/Gb/B in each 2x2 block is at the same position. In this mode, the CFA interpolator simply copies R, G, and B to all points in the 2x2 block. (G is an average of Gb and Gr.)

enum vpsissIpipeDpcOtfModes

On the FLY DPC valid methods.

enum vpsissIpipeDpcOtfModes

Enumerator
VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DPC_OTF_METHOD_MIN 

Adaptive OTF DPC - Min Guard

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DPC_OTF_METHOD_1 

Adaptive OTF DPC - Method 1, refer spec for details

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DPC_OTF_METHOD_2 

Adaptive OTF DPC - Method 2, refer spec for details

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DPC_OTF_METHOD_3 

Adaptive OTF DPC - Method 3, refer spec for details

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DPC_OTF_METHOD_MAX 

Adaptive OTF DPC - Max Guard

enum vpsissIpipeNf2GreenPixType

Enum defining sampling format for the green pixel.

enum vpsissIpipeNf2GreenPixType

Enumerator
VPS_ISS_IPIPE_NF2_GREEN_TYPE_BOX 

Green pixel sampling format is Box, same as Red/Blue

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_NF2_GREEN_TYPE_DIAMOND 

Green pixel sampling format is diamond

enum vpsissIpipeSelDataPath

Valid data path within IPIPE.

enum vpsissIpipeSelDataPath

Enumerator
VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DATA_PATH_RAW_YUV422 

input data is in RAW BAYER format and output data format YUV422

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DATA_PATH_RAW_RAW 

The data are output after the White Balance module. It enables to bypass a large part of the IPIPE module

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DATA_PATH_RAW_DISABLED 

input data is in RAW BAYER format and output is disabled

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_DATA_PATH_YUV422_YUV422 

input data and output data formats are in YUV422 format

enum vpssissIpipeEeMergeMethod

Enum for selecting Edge Enhancer merge method.

enum vpssissIpipeEeMergeMethod

Enumerator
VPS_ISS_IPIPE_EE_MERGE_METHOD_SUM 

The merge method for Edge Enhanced and Sharpener is Max of both

VPS_ISS_IPIPE_EE_MERGE_METHOD_MAX 

The merge method for Edge Enhanced and Sharpener is Sum of both
